Never Asked Questions

This project is really cool. Why it is not part of Spring WS?

Really good question. In fact there is a plan to contribute it to Spring WS in version 2.0. Right now it is better to develop it separately. We can have faster release cycle, we can change the API here and there. After few releases, when the project is more mature it will hopefully be integrated into Spring WS.

I have found a bug, what shall I do?

In case of such unlikely event, please report it here.

I'd like to contribute, how?

Please send me an email to lukas at krecan dot net.
